          solution: "We properly prepare deck surfaces and use high-quality stains designed for foot traffic and weather exposure.",
          urgency: "medium"
        },
        {
          problem: "Paint Cracking in Heat",
          solution: "We use flexible paints and proper preparation techniques that expand and contract with temperature changes.",
