            description: "We use only high-quality exterior paints and materials from trusted brands like Sherwin-Williams and Benjamin Moore."
          },
          {
            title: "Timely Completion",
            description: "We stick to our schedule and complete your project on time, every time."
          }
        ]
      }}
      faqs={[
        {
          question: "How long does an exterior painting project take?",
          answer: "Most exterior projects take 3-7 days depending on the size and complexity. A single-story home typically takes 3-4 days, while a two-story home may take 5-7 days. We provide a detailed timeline during your free estimate."
        },
        {
          question: "Do you work around weather conditions?",
          answer: "Yes! We monitor weather closely and schedule your project during optimal painting weather. We avoid painting in high humidity, extreme heat, or when rain is forecasted."
        },
        {
          question: "What paint brands do you use for exterior work?",
          answer: "We use premium exterior paints from Sherwin-Williams, Benjamin Moore, and PPG. For South Alabama's climate, we often recommend specific weather-resistant and salt air resistant paint systems."
