        },
        {
          question: "How much does exterior painting cost?",
          answer: "Exterior painting costs vary based on home size, surface condition, and paint quality. We provide free, detailed estimates with no obligation. Most single-story homes range from $3,000-6,000, while two-story homes typically cost $5,000-10,000."
